_sText:
Put aim_sdt_warlock.bsp and aim_sdt_warlock.nav into your maps folder. Inorder for the map to function properly, take sdt.vmf and sdt.vtf and put it into your materials folder. You must add the files in the materials folder to your materials folder.

Created by Culda of Source Development Team
This did take me quite awhile, I released many betas before the final release. Here it is, Warlock Final release. I've posted many screenshots.
